<item>
            <title>[LU-2144] segmentation fault when lfsck_xxx run multiple times under the same lctl shell</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2144</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following operations will cause user space segmentation fault:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;#lctl&lt;br/&gt;
lctl &amp;gt; lfsck_start -M lustre-MDT0000&lt;br/&gt;
lctl &amp;gt; lfsck_start -h&lt;br/&gt;
Segmentation fault (core dumped)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
